item.title: A Hard Days Knight
item.description: After many hours I’ve succeeded in reverse engineering a small part of the old DOS game Moonstone!I plan on posting all the gory details, but it’s a bit late at the moment but just running the image viewer script I hacked together and seeing the working result is so pleasing.
